unhindered in his deeds

00:00:14.458 --> 00:00:16.541
Homage to the holy sages

00:00:16.625 --> 00:00:20.166
Homage to the
Western Pure Land of Ultimate Bliss

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:25.583
This represents
the immeasurable virtues of the Pure Land

00:00:25.666 --> 00:00:31.041
Homage to Amitabha Buddha,
