00:00:52.958 --> 00:00:54.083
FUNERAL OFFERING

00:00:54.166 --> 00:00:55.166
My condolences.

00:00:56.458 --> 00:00:57.291
It must be hard.

00:00:58.708 --> 00:00:59.666
Where's An Chi?

00:01:00.375 --> 00:01:03.041
Something came up at school.
She couldn't make it.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.916
She won't even see Hsin-yi off?

00:01:07.416 --> 00:01:09.291
I'm here on her behalf, right?

00:01:12.083 --> 00:01:13.833
Sorry. I have a prenatal check-up.

00:01:13.916 --> 00:01:15.000
I have to go.

00:01:59.333 --> 00:02:00.541
What are you doing here?

00:02:01.416 --> 00:02:03.541
This is the document
you asked me to sign.

00:02:05.166 --> 00:02:07.666
You could've sent it.
No need to come yourself.

00:02:07.750 --> 00:02:08.708
Thank you.

00:02:09.375 --> 00:02:10.958
Won't you invite me up?

00:02:11.625 --> 00:02:13.541
I just came back to grab something.

00:02:13.625 --> 00:02:15.166
Is An Chi home?

00:02:17.916 --> 00:02:19.583
Is that why you came here?

00:02:19.666 --> 00:02:22.458
I really don't understand
what you want with her.

00:02:22.541 --> 00:02:25.208
She told the police everything.
You saw that.

00:02:25.291 --> 00:02:29.250
But her statement didn't explain
why Hsin-yi was tortured to death

00:02:29.333 --> 00:02:31.416
or why Jin Jin is in a coma.

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:32.916
Because she doesn't know.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:35.416
They lived in the same complex
for half a year.

00:02:35.500 --> 00:02:37.125
Surely she knows something?

00:02:37.208 --> 00:02:40.375
Any detail
could be related to Hsin-yi's death.

00:02:40.458 --> 00:02:42.291
Actually, An Chi's gone to the US.

00:02:43.083 --> 00:02:44.833
She's had a hard time emotionally.

00:02:44.916 --> 00:02:46.083
I sent her to get help.

00:02:46.166 --> 00:02:47.625
Her dad's gone with her.

00:02:47.708 --> 00:02:48.791
When was this?

00:02:49.791 --> 00:02:51.000
Last week.

00:02:52.875 --> 00:02:53.875
Huang I-chen.

00:02:55.125 --> 00:02:56.583
What are you hiding from me?

00:02:57.458 --> 00:02:59.000
What have I got to hide?

00:03:00.625 --> 00:03:02.208
I honestly don't understand.

00:03:02.291 --> 00:03:04.083
Can't you just leave An Chi alone?

00:03:04.166 --> 00:03:06.458
Let her be.
She was a victim just like Hsin-yi.

00:03:06.541 --> 00:03:08.041
Leave her alone.

00:04:12.208 --> 00:04:14.041
05 INVESTIGATION NIGHT

00:04:14.125 --> 00:04:15.791
This is a real-life case.

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:19.250
An assailant indiscriminately attacked

00:04:19.333 --> 00:04:21.208
passengers on the MRT.

00:04:21.291 --> 00:04:24.708
The assailant was a young man
weighing less than 60 kg.

00:04:24.791 --> 00:04:28.666
And there were over 70 passengers
in the two carriages at the time.

00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:31.916
But not one of them tried to stop him.

00:04:32.958 --> 00:04:34.833
This is a photo of the crime scene.

00:04:35.708 --> 00:04:37.333
I'd like to pose a question.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:38.958
Imagine this.

00:04:39.041 --> 00:04:41.458
If you were in this carriage that day,

00:04:42.541 --> 00:04:44.833
would you have tried
to subdue the assailant?

00:04:44.916 --> 00:04:46.500
Or, at a time like that,

00:04:46.583 --> 00:04:49.041
would it be wiser to keep your distance

00:04:49.125 --> 00:04:50.791
and protect yourself?

00:04:51.708 --> 00:04:54.708
Either way,
if that was me before I turned 17,

00:04:54.791 --> 00:04:56.625
I would have chosen the latter.

00:05:03.583 --> 00:05:05.333
But when I was 17,

00:05:06.625 --> 00:05:07.916
my life

00:05:08.708 --> 00:05:10.166
took a drastic turn.

00:05:11.416 --> 00:05:12.625
I was kidnapped.

00:05:16.250 --> 00:05:21.375
As a victim and survivor
of a major telecom scam in Southeast Asia,

00:05:21.458 --> 00:05:23.125
I realized one thing.

00:05:23.208 --> 00:05:26.458
Silence and obedience
only encourage evil.

00:05:28.583 --> 00:05:30.041
So we started resisting,

00:05:30.125 --> 00:05:30.958
trying to escape

00:05:31.541 --> 00:05:33.083
and contact the outside world.

00:05:33.875 --> 00:05:37.000
Even though we kept failing,
and were repeatedly punished

00:05:37.083 --> 00:05:39.166
and beaten after we were caughtâ€¦

00:05:39.916 --> 00:05:41.125
Even though in the end,

00:05:41.833 --> 00:05:43.125
my best friend

00:05:44.666 --> 00:05:46.291
lost her life...

00:05:56.458 --> 00:05:59.291
...this seemingly unwise choice

00:05:59.375 --> 00:06:02.250
actually formed an invisible force.

00:06:02.333 --> 00:06:04.916
It was this force
that kept me motivated,

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:07.291
giving me the opportunities and courage

00:06:07.375 --> 00:06:10.041
to seek help during a visit to the bank.

00:06:11.958 --> 00:06:13.583
Although it was a small move,

00:06:13.666 --> 00:06:16.541
it gave the police a clue
and an opportunity

00:06:16.625 --> 00:06:19.000
that led
to the destruction of the notorious

00:06:19.083 --> 00:06:20.875
Southeast Asian crime syndicate.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.083
Because of that,
I am able to stand here

00:06:24.166 --> 00:06:25.958
and talk about my topic today,

00:06:26.416 --> 00:06:28.791
"Be Brave or Be Wise".

00:06:28.875 --> 00:06:30.458
Being wise isn't wrong.

00:06:30.541 --> 00:06:33.000
It's just that this world
needs more brave people.

00:06:33.916 --> 00:06:34.916
Thank you.

00:06:55.875 --> 00:06:57.666
CONGRATULATIONS ON THE PROMOTION

00:06:57.750 --> 00:07:00.666
WELL DONE AN CHI
FOR GETTING INTO YALE LAW SCHOOL

00:07:06.875 --> 00:07:07.916
Congratulations.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.666
You finally won the case.
He got the death penalty.

00:07:10.750 --> 00:07:12.333
Hardly something to celebrate.

00:07:21.208 --> 00:07:22.500
Where's Ms Huang?

00:07:22.583 --> 00:07:24.333
She got promoted and moved offices.

00:07:33.958 --> 00:07:35.916
An Chi's such a talent.

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.708
- Thanks.
- I mean, Yale Law School.

00:07:37.791 --> 00:07:38.875
I know.

00:07:38.958 --> 00:07:41.458
- Apologies. Sorry I'm late.
- It's okay.

00:07:41.541 --> 00:07:43.416
- Where's I-chen?
- She changed offices.

00:07:44.166 --> 00:07:45.916
Your clients are here.

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:50.416
- I'd better get to work. Thank you.
- Okay.

00:07:50.500 --> 00:07:51.708
This way, please.

00:07:55.458 --> 00:07:56.458
In my office.

00:07:58.791 --> 00:08:00.166
THREE MOTHERS' BATTLE

00:08:00.250 --> 00:08:01.958
We won the case, right?

00:08:02.041 --> 00:08:04.291
They want to publish our autobiographies.

00:08:04.375 --> 00:08:06.625
Don't worry, they'll find ghostwriters.

00:08:08.291 --> 00:08:09.958
Write what, exactly?

00:08:10.041 --> 00:08:12.750
Write what happened,
your experiences and the like.

00:08:12.833 --> 00:08:15.833
Wasn't that already covered in the news?

00:08:15.916 --> 00:08:16.958
Yes.

00:08:17.041 --> 00:08:19.500
But there are lots of details
people don't know.

00:08:19.583 --> 00:08:20.500
Like what?

00:08:22.041 --> 00:08:23.125
For example,

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:25.583
how An Chi alerted the police.

00:08:25.666 --> 00:08:26.500
And Jin Jin.

00:08:26.583 --> 00:08:29.833
The syndicate
was using her travel vlog as a tool.

00:08:29.916 --> 00:08:32.625
And how Hsin-yi brought up her late dad

00:08:32.708 --> 00:08:36.208
to alert you.
I think these details are important.

00:08:36.291 --> 00:08:37.791
That's all private, no?

00:08:39.541 --> 00:08:40.666
Sure it is.

00:08:40.750 --> 00:08:43.375
But without these exclusive details,

00:08:43.458 --> 00:08:45.000
no one would buy the book.

00:08:45.083 --> 00:08:47.291
Sounds like exploiting our own children.

00:08:47.875 --> 00:08:49.791
My daughter was a victim too.

00:08:50.208 --> 00:08:51.750
If I saw it as exploitation,

00:08:51.833 --> 00:08:53.083
would I have agreed?

00:08:53.541 --> 00:08:55.791
Hui-chun. You know me.

00:08:55.875 --> 00:08:58.333
You livestream daily
to raise money for Jin Jin.

00:08:58.416 --> 00:08:59.958
Is that exploiting her?

00:09:00.041 --> 00:09:01.750
That's different, okay?

00:09:03.666 --> 00:09:06.791
Look, I'm not doing this for myself.

00:09:07.375 --> 00:09:09.125
If we can publish this book,

00:09:09.208 --> 00:09:10.833
it will be of value to society

00:09:10.916 --> 00:09:13.791
and the royalties
will help ease your financial burdens.

00:09:13.875 --> 00:09:15.666
I promise I'll vet the content.

00:09:16.625 --> 00:09:18.458
Just give me an hour-long interview.

00:09:20.958 --> 00:09:22.666
Can I have an hour with An Chi?

00:09:23.375 --> 00:09:24.875
She's going to Yale.

00:09:24.958 --> 00:09:26.708
How bad can her mental state be?

00:09:26.791 --> 00:09:30.291
I remember she used to be into music.

00:09:30.375 --> 00:09:31.791
When did law become a thing?

00:09:31.875 --> 00:09:33.500
What are you two implying?

00:09:33.583 --> 00:09:35.750
After such a terrifying experience,

00:09:35.833 --> 00:09:37.708
it's normal that she would change.

00:09:37.791 --> 00:09:40.083
Was it her choice, or did you force her?

00:09:40.166 --> 00:09:41.375
Aren't you happy for her?

00:09:41.458 --> 00:09:44.125
She suffered so much
and still managed to alert the police.

00:09:44.208 --> 00:09:46.875
Can you imagine
how much pressure she was under?

00:09:46.958 --> 00:09:49.083
Of course.
So why are you pressuring her--

00:09:49.166 --> 00:09:50.875
How am I pressuring her?

00:09:50.958 --> 00:09:54.583
Come on. We're all happy
she got into college, okay?

00:09:54.666 --> 00:09:56.708
But we'll need time to think about

00:09:57.208 --> 00:09:58.333
publishing this book.

00:09:58.416 --> 00:09:59.416
Forget it.

00:10:00.458 --> 00:10:01.583
Take your time.

00:10:02.583 --> 00:10:04.333
It's not me that needs the money.

00:10:07.208 --> 00:10:08.541
I want the best for you.

00:10:15.875 --> 00:10:17.500
If that's really what you want,

00:10:17.583 --> 00:10:20.000
then spend more time on the civil damages

00:10:20.083 --> 00:10:21.666
rather than this nonsense.

00:10:43.333 --> 00:10:46.125
She kept An Chi
hidden away from everything before,

00:10:46.958 --> 00:10:50.833
saying she didn't want
her daughter to have to relive it all.

00:10:51.416 --> 00:10:52.625
Now the case is over,

00:10:52.708 --> 00:10:55.583
she lets her go on TV every day
and play the victim.

00:10:55.666 --> 00:10:57.583
Why isn't she worried about her now?

00:11:04.250 --> 00:11:06.541
Today's the last day of
the Youth Elite Forum.

00:11:06.625 --> 00:11:09.000
Another round of applause
for everyone on stage.

00:11:32.125 --> 00:11:33.916
Hello, could we interview you?

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:35.125
I'm sorry.

00:11:37.791 --> 00:11:38.791
Congratulations.

00:11:38.875 --> 00:11:39.916
Ms. Wang.

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:41.291
Thank you.

00:11:41.375 --> 00:11:42.916
Can I treat you to dinner?

00:11:43.375 --> 00:11:45.166
Ms. Wang, I have work to do.

00:11:45.625 --> 00:11:46.958
Let's have a chat then.

00:11:47.791 --> 00:11:49.458
Over there. Come on.

00:11:50.041 --> 00:11:51.958
I haven't seen you for a long time.

00:11:57.666 --> 00:11:59.500
You got into such a good college.

00:11:59.583 --> 00:12:01.541
You must have studied really hard.

00:12:02.833 --> 00:12:03.750
It wasn't so bad.

00:12:04.333 --> 00:12:06.000
Nowadays, famous US schools

00:12:06.083 --> 00:12:08.416
want unique and versatile students.

00:12:08.500 --> 00:12:10.833
Like getting into law school,

00:12:10.916 --> 00:12:13.541
I just had to show
what sets me apart from others.

00:12:14.625 --> 00:12:15.875
And what sets you apart?

00:12:19.625 --> 00:12:21.041
That's not what I meant.

00:12:21.125 --> 00:12:23.250
I've always thought you were exceptional.

00:12:23.833 --> 00:12:26.125
Jin Jin always spoke highly of you.

00:12:27.833 --> 00:12:29.750
I found this.

00:12:30.291 --> 00:12:32.250
Since you're going to the US,

00:12:32.833 --> 00:12:34.208
think of it as a memento.

00:12:43.791 --> 00:12:47.375
Actually, I came today
to congratulate you on Jin Jin's behalf.

00:12:48.166 --> 00:12:50.791
She always said you were her best friend.

00:12:55.875 --> 00:12:57.250
One day, she bought

00:12:57.333 --> 00:12:58.916
a bunch of sunflowers home.

00:12:59.833 --> 00:13:01.583
I thought they were for me.

00:13:02.083 --> 00:13:03.250
But she said, "No.

00:13:03.333 --> 00:13:06.000
Tomorrow is An Chi's birthday,
they're for her."

00:13:06.083 --> 00:13:07.833
I was a little disappointed.

00:13:18.708 --> 00:13:20.708
You got into such a good school.

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:24.125
You're going to have a brilliant future.

00:13:25.666 --> 00:13:27.625
Both Jin Jin and Hsin-yi

00:13:28.458 --> 00:13:30.500
would be so happy for you.

00:13:33.625 --> 00:13:35.583
If Jin Jin and Hsin-yi were still alive,

00:13:36.666 --> 00:13:39.166
I know they'd be
pursuing their own dreams too.

00:13:39.250 --> 00:13:40.791
Jin Jin is still alive.

00:13:43.625 --> 00:13:46.041
Or do you think she's as good as dead?

00:13:48.708 --> 00:13:50.250
Ms. Wang, I didn't mean that.

00:13:52.125 --> 00:13:53.541
I know you didn't mean that.

00:13:56.708 --> 00:13:58.791
Ms. Wang, the lights are out. Let's go.

00:14:00.291 --> 00:14:02.125
I keep forgetting to say

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:04.208
thank you.

00:14:04.791 --> 00:14:06.541
Jin Jin only made it back alive,

00:14:06.625 --> 00:14:08.958
because of your bravery in
alerting the police.

00:14:13.791 --> 00:14:14.625
An Chi.

00:14:20.208 --> 00:14:21.250
You forgot this.

00:14:22.875 --> 00:14:24.541
Ms. Wang, thanks for the flowers,

00:14:24.625 --> 00:14:26.875
but you should keep Jin Jin's things.

00:14:50.166 --> 00:14:53.375
ONE MOTHER'S BATTLE

00:15:07.375 --> 00:15:08.208
Eat.

00:15:09.083 --> 00:15:11.041
If you don't eat, you'll starve.

00:15:14.583 --> 00:15:16.875
Do you want me to get out of this alive?

00:15:20.708 --> 00:15:22.625
Die and you'll never see your daughter.

00:15:27.541 --> 00:15:28.958
You didn't know?

00:15:36.666 --> 00:15:37.541
Hello?

00:15:38.000 --> 00:15:39.083
Are you here now?

00:15:39.708 --> 00:15:40.541
We're here.

00:15:41.125 --> 00:15:43.416
Can you tell me
what exactly you are up to?

00:15:44.541 --> 00:15:45.708
Put An Chi on.

00:15:46.750 --> 00:15:48.041
You can say it to me.

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:50.083
I repeat.

00:15:50.708 --> 00:15:52.125
Put An Chi on.

00:15:54.875 --> 00:15:56.041
Hello, Ms. Chao?

00:15:56.625 --> 00:15:57.666
An Chi.

00:15:58.708 --> 00:16:01.666
Okay. Just making sure you're here.

00:16:02.083 --> 00:16:03.125
See you soon.

00:16:19.500 --> 00:16:20.333
Give me some.

00:16:52.208 --> 00:16:53.041
Eason.

00:16:55.333 --> 00:16:56.333
What do you think?

00:16:57.291 --> 00:16:58.291
Beautiful.

00:17:11.250 --> 00:17:12.166
Do you like it?

00:17:12.250 --> 00:17:13.333
Yes.

00:17:14.708 --> 00:17:17.166
But that's okay.
I've got lots of similar outfits.

00:17:18.125 --> 00:17:19.125
It's on me.

00:17:21.833 --> 00:17:23.916
No need, it's not like I can't afford it.

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.416
I've already paid.

00:17:27.708 --> 00:17:29.750
These shoes match your dress.

00:17:30.625 --> 00:17:31.833
Your card, thank you.

00:17:31.916 --> 00:17:33.416
- I want these too.
- Okay, yes.

00:17:40.708 --> 00:17:43.416
You don't have to do this.
It's embarrassing.

00:17:43.500 --> 00:17:44.791
It's fine.

00:17:44.875 --> 00:17:45.708
By the way,

00:17:46.666 --> 00:17:48.166
I'd like to ask a favor.

00:17:48.625 --> 00:17:49.750
Go somewhere with me?

00:17:49.833 --> 00:17:51.250
You'll need to dress up.

00:17:56.000 --> 00:17:57.000
Have a look.

00:17:57.583 --> 00:18:00.000
It's the info we compiled
on the association.

00:18:00.083 --> 00:18:02.083
I had my suspicions before.

00:18:02.166 --> 00:18:04.750
But their accounts were so clean.

00:18:04.833 --> 00:18:06.500
Completely airtight.

00:18:06.583 --> 00:18:10.000
Now that we know they're
using cryptocurrency to launder money,

00:18:10.750 --> 00:18:12.125
we should change tactics.

00:18:12.208 --> 00:18:15.750
I've asked my colleagues
to look for evidence.

00:18:15.833 --> 00:18:19.166
I've even hired a cryptocurrency expert

00:18:19.250 --> 00:18:20.458
as our consultant.

00:18:20.541 --> 00:18:21.416
Don't worry.

00:18:21.500 --> 00:18:23.458
I've called in every favor this time.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:26.416
I'll do my best
to present evidence to the court

00:18:26.500 --> 00:18:27.791
and sue for civil damages.

00:18:28.666 --> 00:18:29.916
- Okay?
- Okay.

00:18:30.666 --> 00:18:33.541
So you mean
you weren't doing your best before?

00:18:37.458 --> 00:18:40.125
What I mean is, as your lawyer,

00:18:41.333 --> 00:18:43.000
I hope that from now on,

00:18:43.625 --> 00:18:45.958
we won't hide anything from each other.

00:18:46.041 --> 00:18:47.291
Okay?

00:18:47.375 --> 00:18:50.166
We never hid anything from you.

00:18:52.708 --> 00:18:53.833
Alright.

00:18:53.916 --> 00:18:55.500
So we can trust each other.

00:18:57.208 --> 00:18:58.500
Then can you tell me

00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:01.083
why Chang Shih-kai is alive?

00:19:03.000 --> 00:19:04.375
What did you do to him?

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:15.041
We found a village in the countryside here

00:19:15.125 --> 00:19:17.041
where villagers worship a goddess.

00:19:17.625 --> 00:19:20.833
This goddess uses witchcraft
to resurrect people.

00:19:20.916 --> 00:19:24.375
So we paid the cops
to get us Chang Shih-kai's corpse,

00:19:24.458 --> 00:19:27.458
then got the goddess to breathe on him.

00:19:31.041 --> 00:19:32.375
And he came back to life.

00:19:35.666 --> 00:19:36.791
It's true.

00:19:45.750 --> 00:19:46.750
Forget it.

